{
  "stem": "12810.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never see them together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was my heartbreak, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That breaks my heart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all my life I carry on with me that heartbreak.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Elizabeth, let's go to 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You finished school--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in Budapest, the very high couture, we make only the film stars and things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was the one who will making [INAUDIBLE], her-- the lady-- the film star's frocks, make it in and take it out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was around them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 35 minutes by train, by [NON-ENGLISH]--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tram, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I go, but it was a very, very high couture.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the name was Vogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they like me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They always said, what a nice little girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I was always around them and pleased them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they liked me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After after when-- when we have to go to the ghetto then I can't do in the tram because then you have to wear the yellow star, you can't go in the train, and I can't walk for-- that far.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they were so clever when the Germans are coming in March 1944 in Hungary, my brother was not home anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was in the [NON-ENGLISH] camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] camp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they-- when they took us to the ghetto, then slowly and slowly the young girls have to go to the-- to the German military factories.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then in the morning, because I work in shift work, so I find a job, because we have to support us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have no money anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They sent us a paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944, in end of March, April.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
